个签:   讲道理/不说故事
简介:   

I look back on the way I was then: a young, stupid kid who committed that terrible crime. I want to talk to him. I want to try and talk some sense to him, tell him the way things are. But I can't. That kid's long gone and this old man is all that's left.很多时候，你愿意讲给别人听的，大概是那些很想，却再也没有机会告诉以前的自己的话吧。


